Subject: Re: [T2] cv joint vibration?

Did you install the lock-washers and backing plates under the CV bolts?
Preferably new lock washers? Apparently, the CV bolts can easily come lose
after maintenance; eventually the CV will fall off, likely sustaining some
damage (ask me how i know).  Check ALL of the CV bolts for tightness.
Install washers and backplates if you don't have them.

Rick
'77 Westy "Pumpkin II"

